title: Ep. - 204 - CO-EXECUTIVE PRODUCER OF JOE MILLIONAIRE
description:
Co-Executive Producer Liz Bronstein discusses her experience as show runner of Fox’s Joe Millionaire, which still holds the record as the highest rated reality finale in the history of television. The basic premise was that bachelor Evan Marriott has inherited millions of dollars and was searching for a potential bride, which was a ruse. The women were not aware that he was is in fact a working-class construction worker. 


Comedian, actor, and host Jamie Kaler reviews Unpolished on TLC, which focuses on the colorful personalities of the women who own and run the trendy Long Island Salon Martone. 



Reality Life with Kate Casey
